COMPOS
{p} {p}
-Intro Compo 4k{p}
Size : 4Kb{p}
Duration : 1 min max.{p}
Obs : Packers are allowed, shouldn't crash the machine{p}
music counts as a positive factor !!!)
{p} {p}
-Intro Compo 64k{p}
Size : 64k{p}
Duration : 5 min max.{p}
Obs : Packers are allowed , shouldn't crash the machine.
{p} {p}
-Demo Compo{p}
Size : 4Mb{p}
Duration : 15 min max.{p}
Obs : Any kind of scripts are allowed (Amiga DOS, Arexx, etc...)
and it shouldn't crash the machine .
{p} {p}
-Mod Compo 1{p}
Music Length: 5min max{p}
Size : 440Kb Max{p}
Obs. : Samples longer that 5secs are not allowed{p}
, all mods will have to be compatible with said "normal" players. ex: {p}
(hippo,eagleplayer,delitraker,modplayer)
{p} {p}
-Mod Compo 2{p}
Music Length: 3min max{p}
Size : 20Kb no máximo{p}
Obs. : The use of packers is allowed and recomended ,{p}
all mods will have to be compatible with said "normal" players.
{p} {p}
